# Build & Run Commands
To build use the `make` command and `./poke` to run the game!


# Controls

## Movement:
- Use the arrow keys
- J K N L 
  
## Menus
- p - to see your current party of pokemon
- b - to open your bag

## Other
- Q - to quit the game
- '<' - to exit most menus
- '>' - to enter building CC & MM
  

# Tiles
- `:` - tall grass
- `.` - open field
- `%` - boulders / edge of map 
- `#` - roads
- `CC`- poke center
- `MM`- poke mart
  
# NPC's
There are a few types of trainers you can fight, each trainer has a different walking path.
Some NPC Trainers movements are static, others will try to actively chase you around the map
- `h` - hiker, the hiker can pass through mountains
- `r` - rival, this trainer will try to catch you around the map
- `n` - normal
- `s` - sentry, will patrol an area